title: “STEWART 6 and 6” Global Radio Show right here on SNN.BZ
text:
NEWS 
Stewart B. Stewart of ALIVE ON SOUTH BEACH, MIAMI global radio its first program today at 6:00AM EST. The show is hosted by ALIVE ON SOUTH BEACH’S own Stewart seen around Miami Beach collecting interviews from the most interesting people alive. 
ALIVE ON SOUTH BEACH can now be heard on our radio station. Here’s the full schedule as of today… 
From midnight to 4AM EST we play inspirational music in 16 languages. 
The day continues with a jazz, latin rythms and classical mix. At midnight we return to inspirational music in 16 languages. 
At 6 AM EST we air the STEWART 6 and 6 Global Radio morning show at SNN.BZ. 
At 6 PM EST we air the STEWART 6 and 6 Global Radio evening show at SNN.BZ
